title: a template
pid: e8d14493-f99b-4a4e-8620-f31e69fca2b3
body: |2-
  try
      Expression,
      ...
      Expression
  of
      SuccessfulPattern1 [Guards] ->
       Expression1;
      SuccessfulPattern2 [Guards] ->
       Expression2
  catch
      TypeOfError:ExceptionPattern1 ->
       Expression3;
      TypeOfError:ExceptionPattern2 ->
       Expression4
  after % Always gets executed. Can't return anything.
       Expr3
  end.
